items.details: 100% raw. Unpasteurized honey. Non GMO Project: Verified. nongmoproject.org. At Wedderspoon we bring you the finest in natural products because we know quality & authenticity matter. We Guarantee: Antibiotic free honey. Hives are made from environmentally friendly material. Our packaging is BPA free. Smooth, creamy, unpasteurized genuine Manuka Honey. From a place where our beekeepers actually talk to their bees and take the time to understand nature to its fullest. Wedderspoon's products have received word of mouth recognition throughout North America due to their outstanding quality and consistency. Wedderspoon's Raw Manuka Honey is sourced from the remote pristine areas of New Zealand's South Island. As part of our tasting methods and to differentiate our potency level, Wedderspoon Manuka Honey is tested for its pollen count, live enzymes, antioxidants and phytochemical components. wedderspoon.com. Product of New Zealand.
